{
  "stem": "26731.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was told one of the physicians went home, and his wife thought he was elsewhere and shot him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mistaken.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes certainly, you could tell he was out of breath.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The woman was disturbed, actually.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right, when I was six years old, 1933, I entered the neighborhood school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You more or less had to go there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you wanted to go elsewhere, you had special permission.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1933, [INAUDIBLE] my father, I remember when I went to school, my father still had the nice apartment.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got my first report card still in the nice apartment, then we had to move.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First we lived [COUGH] in a very nice apartment.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember, I was six years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it didn't have hot water, and it didn't have central heating.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Of course, that wouldn't do, and we moved to a very nice apartment in a different part of town which had all those conveniences.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember of course, even had a maid there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was very close.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I remember actually we were out, on a-- we went out summer, took an apartment in the suburbs away at the lakes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember vaguely where father got the notice that he was dismissed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember that vaguely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not right when he came to power.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was January, but quite early.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I went--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not at all, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Actually there were very few, I would see the Western part-- let's put it this way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Western part of Berlin had the upper and middle class Jews, the central eastern part had the blue collar worker and the people that had immigrated from the east.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was no ghetto as such.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
